name: Michael Hancock
text: Got the $20 family box. It had 2 pan pizzas and bread sticks and wings. It was pretty good. The wings could have used a bit more sauce. I liked the cinnamon bread sticks with the cream cheese sauce. Quick and easy.

name: Andrew Dixon
text: Best service ever!!! Kervin showed up very promptly and was clean shaven and quite handsome. Would order again just to see him! Chairs are kinda heavy though, so be careful not to hurt your shoulder while tossing them!

name: Benjamin Albers
text: I just ordered a pizza from this location, and decided to tip in cash (left on the door).  I typically tip in cash so that the person's tip won't be taxed, and so that they won't have to wait to get the tip.  However, I paid for the order …More

text: Ordered a carryout over the phone last Sunday. Guy that sounded like a teenager was very courteous, offered me a deal and saved me a lot of money! Helped tender my order as well, gave me extra red pepper. Pizza Hut is lucky to have him! Great food, and great location!
